# ================================
# CONFIGURATION NOTES
# ================================

# 1. SECURITY REMINDERS:
#    - Never commit this file with real credentials to version control
#    - Use strong, unique passwords and API keys
#    - Rotate secrets regularly
#    - Limit API key permissions to minimum required

# 2. REQUIRED VARIABLES:
#    - SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_ANON_KEY, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY are required
#    - VITE_SUPABASE_URL, VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY are required for frontend

# 3. OPTIONAL VARIABLES:
#    - Payment, AI, email, monitoring variables are optional
#    - Set only what you need for your deployment

# 4. TESTING:
#    - Test your configuration in a staging environment first
#    - Verify all integrations work before going live

# 5. MONITORING:
#    - Set up monitoring and alerting
#    - Monitor API usage and costs
#    - Set up automated backups

